  "text": "The G+C content of genomic DNA of strain ST07 YE T was determined by the Deutsche Sammlung von Mikroorganismen und Zellkulturen (DSMZ; Braunschweig, Germany). DNA was isolated and purified by chromatography on hydroxyapatite (Cashion et al., 1977) and the G+C content was determined by using HPLC [CITATION_1] . The G+C content of the genomic DNA of strain ST07-YE T was 32.9 mol% ( Table 1 ).",
